name: CREATE: Here=Now
description:
1/2 of the Here=Now cinemagraph series 

A commentary on the current state of artists on Hic Et Nunc, where time and place are often irrelevant when it comes to creating. 

  A transformative take on a photo by Indro Muktiono. The original photo might be included as a part of a future photo collection. Digitally produced.

 1280 × 720 seamlessly looping cinemagraph in MP4 format.
